{"tha-ap187:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap187:0.2":"Kutajapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap187:0.3":"Isimuggadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap187:1.1":"“Udentam sataramsimva, ","tha-ap187:1.2":"pitaramsimva bhanumam; ","tha-ap187:1.3":"Kakudham vilasantamva, ","tha-ap187:1.4":"padumuttaranayakam. ","tha-ap187:2.1":"Isimuggani pisitva, ","tha-ap187:2.2":"madhukhudde anilake; ","tha-ap187:2.3":"Pasadeva thito santo, ","tha-ap187:2.4":"adasim lokabandhuno. ","tha-ap187:3.1":"Atthasatasahassani, ","tha-ap187:3.2":"ahesum buddhasavaka; ","tha-ap187:3.3":"Sabbesam pattapurentam, ","tha-ap187:3.4":"tato capi bahuttaram. ","tha-ap187:4.1":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap187:4.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap187:4.3":"Kappanam satasahassam, ","tha-ap187:4.4":"duggatim nupapajjaham. ","tha-ap187:5.1":"Cattalisamhi sahasse, ","tha-ap187:5.2":"kappanam atthatimsa te; ","tha-ap187:5.3":"Isimuggasanama te, ","tha-ap187:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap187:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap187:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap187:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap187:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma isimuggadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap187:8.1":"Isimuggadayakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}